You are an expert AI assistant for the A.W.A.K.E. project вЂ” a React 19 + TypeScript 5.9 + Vite 7 SPA for Akamai CDN regression observability.

## Project context
- **Repo:** https://github.com/ruake/AWARE  
- **Live:** https://ruake.github.io/AWARE  
- **App directory:** `artifacts/aware-app/`
- All data modules in `artifacts/aware-app/src/lib/`
- Every page wraps `<AppLayout activeHref="...">` and is a default export
- Use wouter's `useLocation()` в†’ `navigate(path)` for SPA navigation
- All pages use inline `style={{}}` with `var(--gcp-*)` CSS vars (NO Tailwind className)
- Charts use Recharts (NOT Google Charts)
- Mockup retired вЂ” only aware-app exists

## Critical rules
1. **`useSyncedUrlState` setter DOES support function updaters**: `setState(prev => ({ ...prev, field: val }))`
2. **Inline styles only** вЂ” never use `className` in page components (shadcn/ui is the exception)
3. **`import.meta.env.BASE_URL`** = `/` in dev, `/AWARE/` in production (GitHub Pages)
4. **Store mutations** вЂ” call `createTestCase()`, `updateTestCase()`, etc. (never access internal stores directly)
5. **`_notify()` + `saveToStorage()`** вЂ” called by public store APIs; don't call manually

## Build commands
```bash
cd artifacts/aware-app
pnpm install
pnpm dev                  # dev server at :5173
pnpm build                # prod build в†’ dist/public/
pnpm run typecheck        # MUST pass before commit
```

## File structure
```
artifacts/aware-app/src/
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ lib/                  # data.ts (barrel), store, runs, testCases, testSuites, promotions, llm, skills, types, nav, urlState
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ components/
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ aware/            # AppLayout, ColumnFilter, CTAStatCard, FilterBar, GenerateWizard, etc.
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ ui/               # shadcn/ui (button, card, badge, dialog, etc.)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ pages/                # Dashboard, Runs, Compare, TestManager, Copilot, etc. (15 pages)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ hooks/                # useSimpleToast, useTestData
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ App.tsx               # wouter Router
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ main.tsx              # Entry point
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ _group.css            # GCP CSS variables
в””в”Ђв”Ђ index.css             # Tailwind imports
```

## Mock data
- 12 runs: `run_892_2341.1.0_prod_<1000-1011>` (in `lib/runs.ts`)
- 15 diff rows: `diff_0` through `diff_14` (in `lib/runs.ts`)
- 4 environments: Prod/Production, Prod/Staging, UAT/Production, UAT/Staging
- Test cases: in-memory store + localStorage (`aware_test_cases_v2`)

## GitHub Pages
- Build copies `dist/public/index.html` в†’ `dist/public/404.html` for SPA routing
- `"packageManager": "pnpm@10.26.1"` required
- Deploy workflow: `.github/workflows/deploy.yml` at repo root
